#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:1
msgid ""
"Add vtkBatch/vtkBatches and improve vtkTablaBasedClipDataSet's performance"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:3
msgid ""
"Batches are a concept that is used in several filters in VTK to enable "
"multithreading. `vtkBatch`/`vtkBatches` are 2 classes that encapsulate the "
"concept of a batch."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:6
msgid ""
"The following filters/data structures have been updated to use `vtkBatch`/"
"`vtkBatches`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:8
msgid "`vtkStaticFaceHashLinks`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:9
msgid "`vtkExtractCells`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:10
msgid "`vtkStructuredDataPlaneCutter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:11
msgid "`vtkPolyDataPlaneCutter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:12
msgid "`vtkPolyDataPlaneClipper`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:13
msgid "`vtkTableBasedClipDataSet`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:15
msgid ""
"Additionally, the performance of `vtkTableBasedClipDataSet` has been "
"improved by ~25%."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:17
msgid "This has been achieved by using with the following ways:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:19
msgid ""
"Used `vtkBatches` for processing also the input points (instead of just the "
"cells), which enables multithreading."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:20
msgid ""
"Reorganized the clip cases table, to enable the removal of several switch "
"cases, and color based checks due to if inside out is on or off."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:22
msgid ""
"Used memcpy instead of for loops to copy point ids to the output cells for "
"the output."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-vtkBatch-and-improve-table-based-clip.md:23
msgid ""
"Created a fast path when a cell is kept or discarded and used the general "
"path only when a cell is clipped."
msgstr ""
